BEGIN_PGML

A current filament arranged in a circular loop of radius [`[$a]`] [`m`] in free space carries a current [`[$i]`] [`A`]. Find the magnitude of the magnetic flux density [`B`] at the center of the loop. 

[`B=`] [_____]{"$Ans"} [`\mu Wb/m^2`]  

